- Use two recursive pointers directly on the original string:
  - Skip non-alphanumeric characters.
  - Compare lowercase versions of characters.
- This reduces the extra space used for storing the cleaned string.

Time Complexity: O(N)
Space Complexity: O(N) (Recursion stack only)
